        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "好的快讯就这些，咱们回到刚才想说的事——高德那个世界模型工坊。",
      "start": 285.68,
      "duration": 7.01,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_021_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_021_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "对，这个我今天必须好好聊一下。",
      "start": 293.169,
      "duration": 2.307,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_022_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_022_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "我看到标题的时候第一反应就是\"这也太离谱了\"，单张5090就能跑小时级的实时交互视频和3D场景，你给我翻译翻译这到底意味着什么？",
      "start": 295.908,
      "duration": 11.233,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_023_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_023_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "说白了，以前世界模型这个赛道基本是大公司的游戏，千卡集群起步、烧钱烧到肉疼，因为生成一个小时的实时可交互3D场景，计算量是海量的。现在高德把它压到一张消费级显卡上就能跑，这不是简单的工程优化，这是底层架构的革命。",
      "start": 307.609,
      "duration": 20.656,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_024_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_024_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "你注意啊，ABot-World Studio这里面的\"World\"不是随便叫的，它生成的不是静态视频，是一个你可以走进去、可以交互的3D世界。",
      "start": 328.755,
      "duration": 13.497,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_025_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_025_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "对，这就是世界模型跟传统视频生成最大的区别。传统视频生成是\"看\"的，世界模型是\"活\"的，它背后有一套对物理规律、对空间关系、对物体交互的理解在里面。你进去推一扇门，门会开；你踢一个球，球会滚动。这种交互性才是它真正的杀手锏。",
      "start": 342.729,
      "duration": 20.743,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_026_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_026_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "那这张牌打出来，对咱们普通人意味着什么？我以后想做个小游戏，是不是连建模都不用学了？",
      "start": 363.89,
